name: Check Made Tote Bag
description:
Carry everything you need in this simple but stylish tote bag!

Black, white and grey check flanellete, lined in calico for extra strength. 40cm × 35cm.

name: Golden Sweetheart Bag
description:
This stylish black and gold handbag is a perfect compliment to any outfit, made from thick black material it is pleated front and back, and is fully lined in black cotton. The silk gold bow completes the look!

Measures approximatley 40cm × 20cm, plus strap.

name: Little Hearts Necklace
description:
This ultra cute heart pendant makes a bright bold statement!

Made from red plastic with a silver metal chain

NOTE: Featured here is the red heart and silver metal chain, however custom necklaces can be made in both other heart colours (purple, yellow, white, blue, pink, green and orange) and a choice of either gold or silver metal chain.

Email perfect.fiction@hotmail.com for ordering details.

This product is also available at Beehive Gallery (441-443 King St Newtown), NSW Australia.

name: Check It Bow
description:
This oversized and playful bow is the perfect hair accessory! Ideal for wearing in a pony tail or bun, this bow adds a youthful touch to every outfit!

Made from black, grey and white check flanellette material. The bow is hand made and sewn to a thick black hair tie.

This product is also available at Beehive Gallery (441-443 King St Newtown) NSW Australia

name: Keyboard Necklace
description:
This stylin' keyboard pendant acts as an ideal fashion feature with any simple t shirt. Great for both guys and girls. Plastic pendant (black and white) on an extra long silver metal chain.

NOTE: Also available in gold metal chain. Email perfect.fiction@hotmail.com for ordering details.
